{"tid":1574910,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔 可唔可以加入標籤功能?","createTime":"2019-09-16T15:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:38:46.000Z","uid":53988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e06867d99f6b886e1762ff09465b6aa99b81ca42","tid":1574910,"uid":53988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:33:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">個標籤功能自己睇到就夠 </span><br />\n可能係個USER名側邊有一格黃/藍/紅色咁 唔使自定義 簡單就夠<br />\n<br />\n是咁的 睇到啲POST 又唔記得啲user名<br />\n搞到成日要起底睇下呢個人係咩立場 好哂時間<br />\n如果個個人好少開post 只會回覆 根本起底都冇用<br />\n<br />\nSBU有用 但係有時又唔想直接block左佢 <br />\n一黎睇唔到佢開左咩POST帶風向<br />\n同埋太多hidden content會好影響閱讀<br />\n而且有時block左好耐 都唔記得左自己當時點解block佢<br />\n<br />\n好多狗+一毛黨係到帶風向 好多巴絲未必會次次都起底<br />\n如果可行既希望連仔可以考慮下<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f4fb3efea6974a5b23e926d255749ddfdf8f68e7","tid":1574910,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acb360278972fff21c713d1e26eae7deda5ad1eb","tid":1574910,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:35:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果機場係春袋 商場就係紅血球<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573192\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573192</a></span><br />\n和理塞 商場篇 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563867\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563867</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">全力攪商場攬炒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1569519\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1569519</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">清算黨鐵商場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1571276\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1571276</a></span><br />\n<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"feac61b030088e3cc51d6674704caad64807b5ee","tid":1574910,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img